PowerTray
========= 

A simple power manager for your systray. Will monitor battery level and suspend/shutdown if needed.

Install
=======

qmake PREFIX=foo
make
make (INSTALL_ROOT=foo) install

Requirements
============

- Qt4
- DBus
- HAL
- System Tray

